    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, powered by the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS valve timing. This example utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to transmit power to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains taut with a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry. Performance is bolstered by significant preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, addressing common E46 weak points. The hydraulic steering rack remains communicative and precise, and the braking system provides consistent bite with minimal fade. A driver-focused machine for those who value mechanical purity and high-RPM engagement.",
