      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? This beauty has been well-loved and is in really solid shape to hit the road today. It runs smooth, looks sharp, and is just waiting for a new home! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 32500.0,
